[
    {
        "text": "On his first full day in Canada,...",
        "startTime": 199,
        "endTime": 1649,
        "slowStartTime": 448,
        "slowEndTime": 2699
    },
    {
        "text": "...Pope Francis delivered a historic apology for the quote,...",
        "startTime": 1741,
        "endTime": 4273,
        "slowStartTime": 2761,
        "slowEndTime": 6635
    },
    {
        "text": "\"...Evil committed by so many Christians against indigenous people.\"",
        "startTime": 4635,
        "endTime": 7638,
        "slowStartTime": 7103,
        "slowEndTime": 11682
    },
    {
        "text": "His week-long trip centers around his response to the treatment of indigenous children...",
        "startTime": 8138,
        "endTime": 12267,
        "slowStartTime": 12357,
        "slowEndTime": 18626
    },
    {
        "text": "...at government-funded schools,...",
        "startTime": 12344,
        "endTime": 13760,
        "slowStartTime": 18666,
        "slowEndTime": 20865
    },
    {
        "text": "...the majority ran by Catholics from the 1800s to the 1900s.",
        "startTime": 13868,
        "endTime": 17479,
        "slowStartTime": 20952,
        "slowEndTime": 26443
    },
    {
        "text": "Chris Livesay is travelling with the Pope.",
        "startTime": 17859,
        "endTime": 19669,
        "slowStartTime": 26938,
        "slowEndTime": 29728
    },
    {
        "text": "At the site of a former residential school in the Canadian city of Masquatchies,...",
        "startTime": 22061,
        "endTime": 26077,
        "slowStartTime": 33241,
        "slowEndTime": 39340
    },
    {
        "text": "...Pope Francis was greeted with sacred drumming and dance,...",
        "startTime": 26373,
        "endTime": 29517,
        "slowStartTime": 39709,
        "slowEndTime": 44500
    },
    {
        "text": "...rituals the Church once sought to erase.",
        "startTime": 29761,
        "endTime": 32410,
        "slowStartTime": 44792,
        "slowEndTime": 48840
    },
    {
        "text": "It was here the Pope issued a historic apology to a crowd of thousands,...",
        "startTime": 33527,
        "endTime": 38100,
        "slowStartTime": 50441,
        "slowEndTime": 57375
    },
    {
        "text": "...most of them indigenous people.",
        "startTime": 38418,
        "endTime": 39960,
        "slowStartTime": 57777,
        "slowEndTime": 60165
    },
    {
        "text": "I am here because the first step of my penitential pilgrimage among you...",
        "startTime": 40133,
        "endTime": 45647,
        "slowStartTime": 60349,
        "slowEndTime": 68695
    },
    {
        "text": "...is that of again asking forgiveness.",
        "startTime": 45817,
        "endTime": 48623,
        "slowStartTime": 68876,
        "slowEndTime": 73159
    },
    {
        "text": "That apology was met with applause from the crowd as was this request,...",
        "startTime": 49233,
        "endTime": 53185,
        "slowStartTime": 74000,
        "slowEndTime": 80003
    },
    {
        "text": "\"...I ask forgiveness.\"",
        "startTime": 53275,
        "endTime": 54819,
        "slowStartTime": 80062,
        "slowEndTime": 82453
    },
    {
        "text": "People were visibly emotional, wiping their tears.",
        "startTime": 54935,
        "endTime": 58167,
        "slowStartTime": 82552,
        "slowEndTime": 87476
    },
    {
        "text": "The Pope was given a traditional headdress to wear after his remarks.",
        "startTime": 58390,
        "endTime": 61947,
        "slowStartTime": 87735,
        "slowEndTime": 93145
    },
    {
        "text": "The Pope began the day visiting what is believed to be a graveyard...",
        "startTime": 62117,
        "endTime": 65072,
        "slowStartTime": 93326,
        "slowEndTime": 97833
    },
    {
        "text": "...for some of the children who never made it home.",
        "startTime": 65159,
        "endTime": 67625,
        "slowStartTime": 97889,
        "slowEndTime": 101662
    },
    {
        "text": "For around a century, more than one hundred fifty thousand native children...",
        "startTime": 67774,
        "endTime": 71358,
        "slowStartTime": 101811,
        "slowEndTime": 107262
    },
    {
        "text": "...were taken from their families to attend government-funded residential schools,...",
        "startTime": 71443,
        "endTime": 75487,
        "slowStartTime": 107315,
        "slowEndTime": 113455
    },
    {
        "text": "...most of them run by the Catholic Church.",
        "startTime": 75806,
        "endTime": 78062,
        "slowStartTime": 113859,
        "slowEndTime": 117318
    },
    {
        "text": "They faced rampant neglect, physical, and sexual abuse,...",
        "startTime": 78336,
        "endTime": 81967,
        "slowStartTime": 117654,
        "slowEndTime": 123175
    },
    {
        "text": "...while being forced to assimilate.",
        "startTime": 82037,
        "endTime": 83959,
        "slowStartTime": 123206,
        "slowEndTime": 126164
    }
]